{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"mutating"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerMigration"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"foreignKeyChecks"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GRDB\/documentation\/GRDB\/DatabaseMigrator","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GRDB16DatabaseMigratorV","text":"DatabaseMigrator"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GRDB\/documentation\/GRDB\/DatabaseMigrator\/ForeignKeyChecks","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GRDB16DatabaseMigratorV16ForeignKeyChecksO","text":"ForeignKeyChecks"},{"kind":"text","text":" = .deferred, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"migrate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GRDB\/documentation\/GRDB\/Database","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GRDB8DatabaseC","text":"Database"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"identifier","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration identifier."}]}]},{"name":"foreignKeyChecks","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This parameter is ignored if the database"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GRDB\/documentation\/GRDB\/Configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" has disabled foreign keys."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".deferred"},{"type":"text","text":" checks have the migration run with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"disabled foreign keys, until foreign keys are checked right before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes are committed on disk. These deferred checks are not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"executed if the migrator is the result of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GRDB\/documentation\/GRDB\/DatabaseMigrator\/disablingDeferredForeignKeyChecks()"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".immediate"},{"type":"text","text":" checks have the migration run with foreign"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"keys enabled. Make sure you only use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".immediate"},{"type":"text","text":" if the migration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"does not perform schema changes described in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/www.sqlite.org\/lang_altertable.html#making_other_kinds_of_table_schema_changes"}]}]},{"name":"migrate","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A closure that performs database operations."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The registered migration is appended to the list of migrations to run:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it will execute after previously registered migrations, and before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"migrations that are registered later."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For example:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["migrator.registerMigration(\"createAuthors\") { db in","    try db.create(table: \"author\") { t in","        t.autoIncrementedPrimaryKey(\"id\")","        t.column(\"creationDate\", .datetime)","        t.column(\"name\", .text).notNull()","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Database operations are wrapped in a transaction. If they throw an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"error, the transaction is rollbacked, migrations are aborted, and the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"error is thrown by the migrating method."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, database operations run with disabled foreign keys, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foreign keys are checked right before changes are committed on disk. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can control this behavior with the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"foreignKeyChecks"},{"type":"text","text":" argument."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Database operations run in the writer dispatch queue, serialized"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with all database updates performed by the migrated "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"DatabaseWriter"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Database"},{"type":"text","text":" argument to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"migrate"},{"type":"text","text":" is valid only during the execution"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the closure. Do not store or return the database connection for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"later use."}]},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No migration with the same identifier as already"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"been registered."}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Precondition"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/grdb\/databasemigrator\/registermigration(_:foreignkeychecks:migrate:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GRDB\/documentation\/GRDB\/DatabaseMigrator\/registerMigration(_:foreignKeyChecks:migrate:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers a migration."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerMigration"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"foreignKeyChecks"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DatabaseMigrator","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GRDB16DatabaseMigratorV"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ForeignKeyChecks","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GRDB16DatabaseMigratorV16ForeignKeyChecksO"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"migrate"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Database","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GRDB8DatabaseC"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"title":"registerMigration(_:foreignKeyChecks:migrate:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:4GRDB16DatabaseMigratorV17registerMigration_16foreignKeyChecks7migrateySS_AC07ForeigngH0OyAA0B0CKctF","modules":[{"name":"GRDB"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GRDB\/documentation\/GRDB","doc:\/\/GRDB\/documentation\/GRDB\/Migrations","doc:\/\/GRDB\/documentation\/GRDB\/DatabaseMigrator"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Registering Migrations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/G